### 測試 1：註冊新帳號
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Ray",
  "email": "esoe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 測試 2：使用者登入
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "esoe@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 測試 3：買入股票 (Transaction 核心測試)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/buy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "esoe@example.com",
  "stock_id": "2330",
  "quantity": 500
}

### 測試 4：賣出股票 (進階功能測試)
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/sell
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "esoe@example.com",
  "stock_id": "2330",
  "quantity": 100
}

### 測試 5：查詢歷史紀錄
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/history
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com"
}

### 測試 6：查詢目前庫存
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/api/inventory
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "esoe@example.com"
}